                <div class="tip-card">
                    <strong>Battle Trance is the entire build.</strong>
                    <p>Without Battle Trance, Bash is just a basic generator. This chest piece is absolutely mandatory &mdash; it provides a massive damage multiplier when at full Fury, which you maintain constantly.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="tip-card">
                    <strong>Paingorger's enables permanent stun lock.</strong>
                    <p>These gloves extend stun duration when you damage stunned enemies. With high attack speed and constant Bash spam, you can keep elites and bosses permanently stunned for the entire fight.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="tip-card">
                    <strong>Focus on single targets for maximum effectiveness.</strong>
                    <p>Bash is a single-target skill. While you can clear packs, the build truly shines against elites and bosses where you can stun lock and deal sustained massive damage.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="tip-card">
